WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:20.864 --> 00:00:21.320
You will remain secure and rest in the shadow of the Almighty, whose power no enemy can withstand.

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:36.340
I will say of the Lord, 'He is my refuge and my fortress, my God in whom I trust with great confidence and on whom I rely.

00:00:36.340 --> 00:00:45.994
' For he will save you from the trap of the fowler and from the deadly pestilence.

00:00:45.994 --> 00:00:55.560
He will cover you and completely protect you with his pinions, and under his wings you will find refuge.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:59.640
His faithfulness is a shield and a wall.

00:01:00.653 --> 00:01:16.669
You will not be afraid of the terror of the night, nor the arrow that flies by day, nor the pestilence that stalks in darkness, nor the destruction and sudden death that lays waste at noon.

00:01:16.669 --> 00:01:27.390
A thousand may fall at your side and 10,000 at your right hand, but no danger will come near you.

00:01:29.605 --> 00:01:40.740
You will only be a spectator as you look on with your eyes and witness the divine repayment of the wicked as you watch safely from the shelter of the Most High.

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:53.665
Because you have made the Lord, who is my refuge, even the Most High, your dwelling place, no evil will befall you, nor will any plague come near your tent.

00:01:53.665 --> 00:02:06.236
For he will command his angels in regards to you to protect and defend and guard you in all your ways of obedience and service.

00:02:06.236 --> 00:02:22.813
They will lift you up in their hands so that you do not even strike your foot against a stone.

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:46.320
You will tread upon the lion and the cobra, the young lion and the serpent.

00:02:46.320 --> 00:02:53.655
You will trample underfoot because he has set his love on me.

00:02:53.655 --> 00:02:57.248
Therefore, I will save him.

00:03:11.046 --> 00:03:11.537
I will set him securely on high because he knows my name.

00:03:11.537 --> 00:03:18.080
He confidently trusts and relies on me, knowing I will never abandon him.

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.160
No, never.

00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:26.702
He will call upon me and I will answer him.

00:03:29.225 --> 00:03:29.480
I will be with him in trouble.

00:03:33.425 --> 00:03:34.778
I will rescue him and honor him with long life.

00:03:36.937 --> 00:03:39.406
I will satisfy him and I will let him see my salvation.

00:03:39.406 --> 00:03:40.091
Amen.

00:03:40.091 --> 00:03:42.446
I love that.

00:03:42.446 --> 00:03:51.960
With long life—long abundant life and abundance to the full until it overflows.

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:57.966
Overflow life, not just barely getting by life, but overflow life and abundant life.

00:04:07.335 --> 00:04:07.680
How many are here?

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:09.223
Well, good morning, family.

00:04:09.223 --> 00:04:10.400
Praise the Lord.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:15.194
It's evening time, but I like saying good morning.

00:04:15.194 --> 00:04:19.540
It's the start of a new day.

00:04:19.540 --> 00:04:21.835
So, we're excited to be here tonight.

00:04:21.835 --> 00:04:23.914
We have some things to pray over.

00:04:23.914 --> 00:04:32.800
We're excited to see that so far we don't have anybody acting like a fool about the food stamps and all that in our nation.

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:37.983
No riots from what I can see, so I believe our prayers are working.

00:04:41.924 --> 00:04:47.330
We see that we've had a major terrorist plot that was scheduled for yesterday or this weekend brought down by our FBI.

00:05:04.845 --> 00:05:05.140
And we give all the glory to God for that because I believe that prayer has changed things.

00:05:05.140 --> 00:05:10.124
I want to give God all the glory for that.

00:05:10.124 --> 00:05:22.751
Look, folks, I believe when we come together and do this prayer together, that's what we're here for: that we're able to uncover the rats in our government and in our country, that we have authority over this.

00:05:22.751 --> 00:05:25.526
Diana is going to read this authority today.

00:05:29.871 --> 00:05:32.907
You know the scriptures, and my sister Billye Brim, she had this book and she has the prayer.

00:05:32.907 --> 00:05:39.145
Diana is going to read the prayer of what Sister Billye has, how we all prayed together every day.

00:05:39.145 --> 00:05:47.240
But just going over this so that you can practice this with your family using scripture to combat the devil.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:55.880
You don't stand alone; you stand with a pillar, and that's the word of God.

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:03.213
And that's the only thing that's ever going to set you free.

00:06:03.213 --> 00:06:10.040
You'll know the truth, and the truth of God's word will set you free and make you free.

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:23.213
The only thing that's ever going to set you free is God's word—knowing Him, who you are in Christ, knowing the authority of the believer, what we have in Christ, and what he paid for us.

00:06:23.213 --> 00:06:28.810
What did he do for us on that cross when he said, 'It is finished'?

00:06:28.810 --> 00:06:31.008
What did he say was finished?

00:06:31.008 --> 00:06:42.840
Everything that he set out to do so that we have an abundant life—that you're healed, you're whole, you're well, you're forgiven of your sins—everything he set out to do, it is finished.

00:06:56.138 --> 00:06:56.480
And I believe we have authority over the devil.

00:07:03.400 --> 00:07:05.600
And like I said, I don't ever really sponsor books or whatever; I'm just trying to tell you what we read.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:08.870
You know, people go, 'Well, you're trying to help sell.

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:14.354
' No, I'm not selling books; I'm trying to tell you what works.

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:19.516
And we read books that work.

00:07:19.516 --> 00:07:22.870
And if we don't believe it works, we don't read it.

00:07:22.870 --> 00:07:24.660
It's kindling for the fireplace.

00:07:24.660 --> 00:07:30.800
I'm just telling you, I don't waste my time with it.

00:07:41.589 --> 00:07:41.771
But I believe Sister Billye has a nugget here and I encourage you—you can't find it anywhere.

00:07:45.445 --> 00:07:45.700
