00:08:46.935 --> 00:08:51.040
And so I was like, 'Hey, this is a blessing.

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:54.650
' I've never had it before and I feel good after taking it.

00:08:54.650 --> 00:08:56.130
She had some.

00:08:56.130 --> 00:08:59.750
So I said I tried some today.

00:08:59.750 --> 00:09:01.874
It does—it makes you feel good.

00:09:01.874 --> 00:09:09.187
No, I'm not getting into network marketing, but I'm telling you, thank you to whoever sent that.

00:09:15.280 --> 00:09:15.680
So kind.

00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:16.880
