01:35:35.400 --> 01:35:58.429
I told Diana, I said we average—if I do an average of two hours of video a day, if I do these live streams five times a week—I told her, I said, 'I do an average of 50-some hours a month of prayer videos with y'all.

01:35:58.429 --> 01:36:05.250
' 50-some hours of videos because we were doing the math on it.

01:36:09.594 --> 01:36:11.309
