01:36:29.740 --> 01:36:30.165
I don't know you at all.

01:36:30.165 --> 01:36:42.617
When you come in public, I go—I met a guy yesterday; he goes, 'Oh, I watch you.

01:36:42.617 --> 01:36:48.152
I know you so well,' and I'm like, 'I don't know you at all.

01:36:48.152 --> 01:36:54.570
' And it's awkward for me, so I'm like, 'Okay, well, praise God.

01:36:54.570 --> 01:36:59.600
