01:41:19.649 --> 01:41:28.909
But you've got to do what nobody else is willing to do to get there.

01:41:41.333 --> 01:41:42.230
You can't act like that and just have a mentality of 'I deserve it; it's mine.

01:41:42.240 --> 01:41:44.150
' You've got to train like a champion.

01:41:44.150 --> 01:41:46.660
You've got to train like a champion spiritually.

01:41:46.660 --> 01:41:54.827
If you want what a champion has, you've got to train like a champion does.

01:42:09.107 --> 01:42:09.633
