01:42:14.200 --> 01:42:20.800
And the Lord told me, he said, 'It's not required for me to do it.

01:42:32.240 --> 01:42:32.680
You have to be as dedicated as an Olympian.

01:42:32.680 --> 01:42:34.000
' Yes.

01:42:45.071 --> 01:42:45.360
It's not just going to happen, Brandon.

01:43:03.063 --> 01:43:03.406
To come up higher requires more of you, but it's not something you deserve.

01:43:03.406 --> 01:43:06.329
