It's all on the side over here, and it's like there's an infection on this toe.

01:56:19.120 --> 01:56:27.135
The Lord Jesus, I believe, is wanting to heal this toe right now in the name of Jesus.

01:56:27.135 --> 01:56:44.240
You have an infection in your big toe on your foot, and I call healing and wholeness and wellness over this toe in Jesus' name.

01:56:46.400 --> 01:56:47.180
All infection be gone.

01:56:51.920 --> 01:56:52.120
I call a brand new toenail.

01:56:58.764 --> 01:57:00.818
It looks almost like it has gangrene on it.

01:57:01.160 --> 01:57:02.653
Like it's rotten.

01:57:02.653 --> 01:57:03.667
Maybe from diabetes.

01:57:03.667 --> 01:57:06.973
Yeah, that's it.

01:57:06.973 --> 01:57:09.448
Do you hear me?

01:57:09.448 --> 01:57:11.560
I see it.

01:57:11.560 --> 01:57:17.000
As the Lord said, 'That's it.

01:57:17.000 --> 01:57:19.980
' It's like an infection from diabetes.

01:57:19.980 --> 01:57:20.640
That's amazing.

01:57:20.640 --> 01:57:26.616
I heard in the spirit, he said, 'That's it.

01:57:26.616 --> 01:57:26.884
You did it.

01:57:26.884 --> 01:57:27.152
That's it.

01:57:27.152 --> 01:57:29.570
That's what I'm asking for.

01:57:29.570 --> 01:57:34.600
' It's an infection from diabetes.

01:57:34.600 --> 01:57:38.822
You've got this toe that is trying to get gangrene.

01:57:38.822 --> 01:57:41.689
It's rot from diabetic nerve damage and damage from diabetes on your toe.

01:57:46.933 --> 01:57:54.640
In fact, the doctor is talking about removing—I hear the spirit of the Lord say the doctor is telling you they're going to remove your toe.

01:57:54.640 --> 01:58:05.590
But I speak to that toe to be healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

01:58:05.600 --> 01:58:17.430
Every bit of that infection, every bit of that gangrene, every bit of that black—it's like black all over; it looks really nasty.

01:58:17.440 --> 01:58:23.215
I speak in the name of Jesus for healing and wholeness and wellness.

01:58:29.200 --> 01:58:29.372
And it's tried to move over to the next toe slightly.

01:58:29.372 --> 01:58:30.748
It's over on the next toe.

01:58:41.989 --> 01:58:42.166
You're saying, 'No, you're not taking my toe.

01:58:42.166 --> 01:58:43.606
You're not taking my toe.

01:58:43.606 --> 01:58:44.840
' That's what you keep saying.

01:58:44.840 --> 01:58:45.900
We thank you, Holy Spirit.

01:58:45.900 --> 01:58:48.415
You're touching that toe right now in the name of Jesus.

01:58:48.415 --> 01:58:53.176
All of it, the infection, clearing it out.

01:58:55.131 --> 01:59:05.451
And Father, I thank you by the time they get up in the morning, it could be completely healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus, restoring everything the devil's tried to steal.

01:59:05.451 --> 01:59:12.960
Healing and wholeness and wellness over that toe in Jesus' mighty name.

01:59:12.960 --> 01:59:14.596
That's the glory of God today.

01:59:18.840 --> 01:59:19.413
I believe the glory of God is on you today.

01:59:20.560 --> 01:59:21.022
I believe it.

01:59:23.756 --> 01:59:23.880
The toe will be restored in Jesus' name.

01:59:30.800 --> 01:59:31.107
And Father, I thank you.

01:59:31.107 --> 01:59:35.680
Not only do you heal the toe, but you heal the diabetes also.

01:59:35.680 --> 01:59:39.976
We speak healing and wholeness and wellness over diabetics in Jesus' name.

01:59:39.976 --> 01:59:44.227
We speak deliverance over diabetes from type 2 to type 1.

01:59:45.062 --> 01:59:47.540
I speak healing and wholeness and wellness over that pancreas in Jesus' name.

01:59:47.540 --> 01:59:52.627
Father, redeem from the curse of the law that the blood sugar straightens out.

02:00:00.354 --> 02:00:10.380
I call the fire of God over that pancreas, over that digestive system in the name of Jesus and these weight issues of obesity.

02:00:21.440 --> 02:00:24.071
I speak in the name of Jesus healing and wholeness and wellness from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

02:00:24.071 --> 02:00:26.660
We call blood sugars to line up.

02:00:26.660 --> 02:00:30.994
We call restoration of the blood in Jesus' name.

02:00:30.994 --> 02:00:36.566
Nerve damage be healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

02:00:36.566 --> 02:00:39.044
Restoration of all things even in the calves and the legs.

02:00:39.044 --> 02:00:40.516
Nerve damage being healed and whole.

02:00:44.660 --> 02:00:44.960
I see healing and wholeness in the fingers in Jesus' name.

02:00:44.960 --> 02:00:50.948
I speak over the pancreas to be healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

02:00:50.948 --> 02:00:56.968
Some of you, this is a demonic spirit; you had a cultic assignment assigned to you through an elder.

02:01:15.688 --> 02:01:15.800
I see this demon.

02:01:29.471 --> 02:01:29.702
It looks like a python.

02:01:31.320 --> 02:01:37.600
You had hands laid on you and there is an impartation of a demonic spirit that has been set on you.

02:01:40.080 --> 02:01:42.107
And the Lord Jesus Christ rebuke that devil in Jesus' name.

02:01:46.640 --> 02:01:49.222
And you're free from it from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

02:01:49.960 --> 02:01:50.710
I see it.

02:01:50.710 --> 02:01:55.978
I don't know who laid hands on you, but they shouldn't have; it was imparted.

02:01:55.978 --> 02:01:57.850
Do not let people touch you unaware quickly.

02:01:57.850 --> 02:02:01.947
Well, there's this scripture—Love, help me with this scripture.

02:02:01.947 --> 02:02:09.000
Don't let people touch you, and you don't know those that are laboring among you.

02:02:09.000 --> 02:02:09.686
There's a scripture.

02:02:14.480 --> 02:02:14.756
I need you to help me with that scripture.

02:02:14.756 --> 02:02:16.964
'Lay hands on no man suddenly.

02:02:16.964 --> 02:02:20.360
' Thank you, Holy Ghost.

02:02:24.040 --> 02:02:24.417
The Lord just said it.

02:02:24.417 --> 02:02:26.220
'Lay hands on no man suddenly.

02:02:26.220 --> 02:02:29.120
' That's what the scripture is.

02:02:29.120 --> 02:02:42.903
And you shouldn't let people be just touching you all the time.

02:02:42.903 --> 02:02:45.400
This was imparted by somebody.

02:02:45.400 --> 02:02:46.280
1 Timothy 5:22.

02:02:46.280 --> 02:02:54.600
'And lay hands suddenly on no man, neither be partaker of other men's sins; keep thyself pure.

02:02:54.600 --> 02:02:56.851
' Don't be touching people quickly.

02:02:57.120 --> 02:03:01.382
Know those that labor among you.

02:03:01.382 --> 02:03:02.431
This was imparted.

02:03:02.431 --> 02:03:04.120
This is a demonic spirit.

02:03:04.547 --> 02:03:10.720
I see it, and it looked almost like a demon of black electricity.

02:03:10.720 --> 02:03:22.686
God's electricity is white, like lightning bolts, but this was a demonic electricity with yellow eyes, shaped like electricity, and it went through you like a current.

02:03:22.686 --> 02:03:29.360
This demonic spirit of diabetes was assigned to you demonically, and the Lord Jesus wants to set you free from it.

02:03:29.360 --> 02:03:32.000
That is such a strong word.

02:03:34.680 --> 02:03:35.520
I see it so clearly.

02:03:36.640 --> 02:03:41.977
I don't know who this is, but I know you're watching and the Lord is setting you free.

02:03:55.097 --> 02:03:55.320
This is a demonic spirit that has been assigned by the laying on of hands.

02:03:58.580 --> 02:04:01.240
Just as the Holy Ghost can be imparted, the devil can be imparted.

02:04:01.240 --> 02:04:02.264
Do you understand?

02:04:06.807 --> 02:04:07.000
Don't let people touch you all the time.

02:04:07.000 --> 02:04:19.768
When people say, 'I have to pray for you,' I tell them, 'Do not touch my family or me without the Holy Ghost leading you.

02:04:19.768 --> 02:04:25.027
' People say I got aggressive; I said I'd break their fingers.

02:04:32.020 --> 02:04:32.250
I meant it.

02:04:33.280 --> 02:04:40.291
I don't mean to be rude, but I'm telling you, don't touch me unless the Holy Spirit leads me to let you.

02:04:40.291 --> 02:05:03.240
Even with guest speakers at the front of the church, you see Brandon Biggs and think, 'Don't go up there,' because the Holy Spirit said, 'Don't let them touch you.

02:05:03.240 --> 02:05:06.000
' I don't let everyone touch me.

02:05:08.080 --> 02:05:09.500
I only have certain people I go to.

02:05:10.920 --> 02:05:16.969
I don't let just anyone pray for me; I let the Holy Spirit lead me.

02:05:16.969 --> 02:05:21.870
Sister Lynn was up there, and it was said, 'You can have her pray for you.

02:05:21.870 --> 02:05:32.070
' Things are imparted by the laying on of hands, both good and bad.

02:05:43.556 --> 02:05:43.832
You need wisdom concerning this, and most people do not have it.

02:05:43.832 --> 02:05:45.212
They trust too easily.

02:05:47.815 --> 02:05:48.170
You must have wisdom.

02:05:48.170 --> 02:05:57.360
Don't allow everyone to impart into you unless you feel led by the Spirit of God.

02:05:57.360 --> 02:06:12.720
I am trying to tell you from experience: do not let people touch you unless you know them or are familiar with the Holy Ghost in them.

02:06:12.720 --> 02:06:13.395
Be watchful.

02:06:31.455 --> 02:06:31.750
I am telling you this because of my own past ignorance.

02:06:31.750 --> 02:06:33.225
Be smart about this.

02:06:49.440 --> 02:06:49.974
I just saw a demonic spirit, looking like a black electric devil, that was imparted to someone.

02:07:00.907 --> 02:07:01.138
It went into you and caused diabetes, and it's trying to take your toes.

02:07:01.138 --> 02:07:01.369
Resist it.

02:07:01.369 --> 02:07:02.425
Say, 'I repent.

02:07:02.425 --> 02:07:05.485
' Father, we call it to go out in Jesus' name.

02:07:05.485 --> 02:07:11.830
We speak to you; you are free in the name of Jesus.

02:07:11.840 --> 02:07:13.240
Demonic spirit, leave them.

02:07:13.240 --> 02:07:17.400
Spirit of diabetes, be healed and whole in Jesus' name.

02:07:17.400 --> 02:07:21.813
Do not walk in fear, but be watchful and know those who labor among you.

02:07:21.813 --> 02:07:25.573
That was a very strong word.

02:07:25.573 --> 02:07:30.120
The other part concerned heart problems and heart palpitation problems.

02:07:35.211 --> 02:07:35.446
You didn't know why these palpitation problems started.

02:07:35.897 --> 02:07:37.200
You started having a heart arrhythmia.

02:07:47.600 --> 02:07:48.040
I hear the word 'heart arrhythmia'—irregular heartbeats.

02:07:48.040 --> 02:07:51.150
It is all by impartation.

02:07:53.931 --> 02:08:00.000
Some may not agree with all of it, but concerning certain individuals, this relates to the diabetic issue.

02:08:04.538 --> 02:08:07.420
I believe it is for one person, but if you receive it for yourself, say, 'I believe I am healed.

02:08:07.420 --> 02:08:09.703
' Piggyback on the word.

02:08:09.703 --> 02:08:15.400
There is an impartation you got from the demonic even concerning your heart.

02:08:15.400 --> 02:08:18.480
The heartbeats are bad; they are flutters.

02:08:25.493 --> 02:08:25.716
I see it clearly: heart flutters.

02:08:26.160 --> 02:08:29.707
You have been dealing with this for a while, but there is an expiration date on what you are going through.

02:08:29.707 --> 02:08:31.027
Today is that expiration date.

02:08:33.717 --> 02:08:42.200
The demonic spirit sent to destroy you, God is going to turn around for His glory, and you will deliver many people with the same issues.

02:08:42.400 --> 02:08:46.629
I also see spirits of depression that have been imparted.

02:09:01.548 --> 02:09:01.792
You have been walking with a cloud of darkness over your head.

02:09:01.792 --> 02:09:06.200
You feel like Eeyore from the Winnie the Pooh cartoon, thinking everything is bad.

02:09:06.200 --> 02:09:11.011
There is a darkness on your mind, but the Lord is delivering you and turning that frown upside down.

02:09:19.049 --> 02:09:20.511
The Lord says it is time for days of great joy in your household.

02:09:23.660 --> 02:09:27.440
You have been sad long enough; this assignment of depression, anxiety, and worry is over.

02:09:27.440 --> 02:09:31.550
That imparted devil is going away now in Jesus' name.

02:09:31.550 --> 02:09:35.187
He gives us a spirit of joy, peace, love, and a sound mind.

02:09:38.040 --> 02:09:39.080
You may ask where your joy has gone.

02:09:47.120 --> 02:09:48.675
The Lord also said this has to do with finances.

02:09:51.920 --> 02:09:53.284
You are imparting your tithe into bad ground.

02:09:53.633 --> 02:10:01.093
I am going to be bold and say it: you are tithing to a church that is not frugal with your money.

02:10:01.093 --> 02:10:06.045
Not all ground produces the same—some thirty, some sixty, some a hundredfold.

02:10:15.204 --> 02:10:15.413
You have had questions about where you have been giving because something didn't feel right.

02:10:19.542 --> 02:10:19.933
You felt there was corruption, but you stayed out of loyalty.

02:10:23.787 --> 02:10:28.830
You are sowing into cankerworms, and they are eating your harvest because you keep sowing into ground where they are doing bad things with your money.

02:10:28.830 --> 02:10:29.370
Look for fruit.

02:10:29.370 --> 02:10:33.806
Fruit is a representation of the root.

02:10:33.806 --> 02:10:36.022
If the fruit is bad, the root is rotten.

02:10:36.022 --> 02:10:37.514
Look at what the fruit does.

02:10:37.514 --> 02:10:38.896
Are people getting set free?

02:10:38.896 --> 02:10:50.320
Are they learning to stand on their authority as believers and fight the good fight of faith?

02:10:50.320 --> 02:10:52.897
Do you understand what I am saying?

02:10:57.964 --> 02:10:58.448
I am trying to translate what I see in the spirit into English.

02:10:58.448 --> 02:11:07.560
When I am relaying a vision, I often check if it makes sense because I am looking into the spirit realm.

02:11:07.560 --> 02:11:08.960
You communicated it well.

02:11:08.960 --> 02:11:09.852
Thanks, love.

02:11:10.184 --> 02:11:15.825
I see a tree, and I could spend all night describing every vision I have seen.

02:11:15.825 --> 02:11:22.640
The Lord said this tree would bear much fruit if you do that.

02:11:28.240 --> 02:11:29.413
I see a ministry, and the Lord sees this ministry.

02:11:29.609 --> 02:11:34.760
I see a tree and the tree goes up like this; it's big and it's green.

02:11:34.760 --> 02:11:37.560
It looks like a massive oak tree.

02:11:37.560 --> 02:11:41.325
It's a beautiful tree on the outside when you're glancing at it.

02:11:41.325 --> 02:11:48.480
But the tree is rotten with worms, termites, and infection.

02:11:57.240 --> 02:11:59.960
You can actually touch it and the tree starts to crumble inside.

02:11:59.960 --> 02:12:08.960
But then you look up inside the fruit of the tree, and there are worms and bird holes; the fruit is rotten, but the tree from a glance looks beautiful.

02:12:13.432 --> 02:12:13.620
This is a ministry that you're giving into.

02:12:21.520 --> 02:12:21.840
This is a big tree.

02:12:26.000 --> 02:12:26.500
You understand?

02:12:26.500 --> 02:12:31.493
It wasn't a little shrub; this is something big.

02:12:41.720 --> 02:12:41.902
But there's something going on in the core of it, and so it is rotten inside.

02:12:41.902 --> 02:12:42.813
So watch the fruit.

02:12:42.813 --> 02:12:46.720
Watch the fruit of where you give.

02:12:59.760 --> 02:13:00.080
You say, "Well, what's going on with my money, I guess?

02:13:15.560 --> 02:13:15.753
" I remember when the Lord said to us—we were sowing into a particular church, and the pastor was dealing with adultery.

02:13:15.753 --> 02:13:17.680
He was keeping it secret for two years.

02:13:17.680 --> 02:13:24.453
Two years messing around on his wife, and it started trickling over the congregation.

02:13:24.453 --> 02:13:29.726
The people on staff started having adulterous affairs.

02:13:29.726 --> 02:13:34.996
He was like, "Man, all these marriages are falling apart.

02:13:38.380 --> 02:13:41.920
What is going on with sister so-and-so cheating on her husband and brother so-and-so cheating on his wife?

02:13:41.920 --> 02:13:46.960
" It was spreading, and you go into the congregation and realize something's going on.

02:13:46.960 --> 02:13:56.463
Men were dealing with so much pornography and sexual perversion, and you're thinking, "Something's going on; this isn't normal.

02:13:56.463 --> 02:13:57.994
" We started watching.

02:13:59.510 --> 02:13:59.885
It was hidden.

02:14:09.050 --> 02:14:13.255
I started watching, and the Lord said, "Start praying into this.

02:14:15.436 --> 02:14:19.307
I want to show you something," because I was dealing with stuff I never dealt with before.

02:14:19.307 --> 02:14:22.104
I told her, "Something's wrong, Diana, because this is a spirit.

02:14:22.104 --> 02:14:22.760
What is this?

02:14:25.200 --> 02:14:29.160
" I started backing away from the tithe and from other things, and the Lord started teaching us stuff.

02:14:30.510 --> 02:14:42.507
I'm trying to tell you this by the Spirit of God.

02:14:53.440 --> 02:14:53.700
The Lord started giving us dreams.

02:14:53.700 --> 02:14:56.080
We started praying into it.

02:14:56.080 --> 02:15:05.182
What I'm trying to tell you is that you need to know those who labor among you.

02:15:05.182 --> 02:15:11.093
Do not trust so easily.

02:15:11.093 --> 02:15:17.302
As it was with the head of the church, it started trickling down to where you tithe and where you go to church.

02:15:17.587 --> 02:15:18.913
You say, "I never dealt with this before.

02:15:18.913 --> 02:15:34.350
" I'm not blaming only the head of that church, but if you start seeing a lot of other people in that church dealing with the same thing, you start questioning yourself.

02:15:34.350 --> 02:15:44.950
Put it together; it's a picture, and the Lord is trying to warn you.

02:15:49.347 --> 02:15:49.920
Now, it's not always that way.

02:15:49.920 --> 02:15:58.893
Sometimes it's just you, and you have to deal with your flesh in other areas.

02:15:58.893 --> 02:16:14.288
It's all flesh, don't get me wrong, but I'm saying it starts trickling down onto the congregation and you can start to see it.

02:16:14.288 --> 02:16:17.098
That's what it was in this circumstance.

02:16:18.040 --> 02:16:27.592
It starts on the fruit of the tree and is distributed among the people, and you realize something is not right here.

02:16:29.805 --> 02:16:32.300
I say that's why poop rolls downhill; that's what happens.

02:16:32.300 --> 02:16:34.249
I'm just trying to be real with you.

02:16:34.249 --> 02:16:36.125
It's stuff we've learned.

02:16:48.359 --> 02:16:48.572
You start watching and realize something isn't right.

02:16:48.572 --> 02:16:49.212
Be watchful.

02:16:49.212 --> 02:16:56.960
Seeds are very important where you sow financially and who is laying hands on you.

02:16:56.960 --> 02:16:58.719
Watch those things in these last days.

02:16:58.719 --> 02:17:05.338
Do not trust so easily.

02:17:05.338 --> 02:17:06.204
Be watchful.

02:17:06.204 --> 02:17:14.668
That's why Diana and I will sow a little bit to test the ground.

02:17:14.668 --> 02:17:25.267
We watch the ground and say, "Okay, we've tested it; now be watchful over that.

02:17:25.267 --> 02:17:30.173
" Then we say, "Show us, Holy Spirit, how this ground is.

02:17:30.173 --> 02:17:37.893
" When you trust it, then you come and dump a lot.

02:17:38.542 --> 02:17:44.088
You say, "Listen, here is more," and I see how you handle that.

02:17:44.088 --> 02:17:52.952
If they don't handle it right, you don't do that anymore, or you only do what the Spirit of God leads you.

02:17:53.880 --> 02:17:58.470
I believe in tithing.

02:18:03.160 --> 02:18:07.831
I believe in sowing and reaping, and I believe whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap.

02:18:19.280 --> 02:18:19.600
I believe in thirty, sixty, and a hundredfold.

02:18:19.600 --> 02:18:34.146
I'm required to tithe by my Holy Father because I'm helping the kingdom, but I always watch how I sow my seeds.

02:18:34.146 --> 02:18:48.377
The Lord has blessed me, and He'll say, "Brandon, don't do that again.

02:18:48.377 --> 02:18:49.719
" Find the good ground.

02:18:49.719 --> 02:18:52.474
Be smart with where you give.

02:18:58.507 --> 02:18:59.173
It's more important than you realize.

02:18:59.173 --> 02:19:07.080
People flippantly just do things, but it's the difference between life and death for some.

02:19:07.080 --> 02:19:11.850
You need to hear me; I'm telling you something I've learned.

02:19:11.850 --> 02:19:19.719
Do not give by emotion; give by the Spirit of the Lord.

02:19:25.369 --> 02:19:25.480
You can be led by emotion, and people will manipulate you.

02:19:31.334 --> 02:19:33.707
A good preacher praying—praise the Lord—might say, "Oh, we have a need," while playing the keyboard, and you feel you have to sow a seed.

02:19:39.800 --> 02:19:39.960
I'm not trying to meddle, but there is spiritual, charismatic flakiness.

02:19:39.960 --> 02:19:42.700
It is always a biblical principle to give.

02:19:42.700 --> 02:20:01.707
Give, and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over.

02:20:01.707 --> 02:20:24.827
But know those who labor among you and where you are giving, knowing how you sow a seed.

02:20:24.827 --> 02:20:32.000
If you have a need, sow a seed.

02:20:44.044 --> 02:20:44.342
That's why we are strategic in everything we do.

02:20:44.342 --> 02:20:51.584
If we don't see fruit there, we don't do it ever again.

02:20:51.584 --> 02:21:07.120
There have been times where we have tested the ground and there has been no fruit, almost to the point where it is devoured in front of your face.

02:21:07.120 --> 02:21:08.537
We don't do that again.

02:21:08.537 --> 02:21:13.147
Be like a good farmer.

02:21:18.760 --> 02:21:19.173
A farmer knows where to plant the seed to get a good harvest.

02:21:19.173 --> 02:21:30.160
He's not going to put it in a river bottom because it will wash away.

02:21:36.760 --> 02:21:53.627
